==Chinese==
===[[wikipedia:Taiwanese Mandarin|Taiwanese Mandarin]]===
Pinyin: sān K chǎnyè

===Etymology===
From the Japanese term "[[3K]]", which stands for '''k'''itsui ([[きつい]] difficult, hard), '''k'''itanai ([[汚い]] dirty) and '''k'''iken ([[危険]] dangerous).

===Noun===
'''3K[[產業]]'''
#[[3D jobs]] (dirty, dangerous and difficult jobs)

===Alternate forms===
* [[3K产业]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
* 3K行業
* 三K行業

